      "body" : "I think we should keep `-usehd=1` for now.\r\nWe need to think about ... \r\n\r\n1. if and how we are going to allow HD for already existing wallets\r\n2. How a user could input a seed (xpriv) during hd wallet creation (I guess a config argument `-hdmasterkey=<xpriv>` would not be the best way to do this, adding an RPC call would allow to pass in a master key at the stage where the wallet has already been created).",
